</blockquote><br />
<a href="http://www.americanheritage.com/travel/articles/web/20060407-pizza-italian-food-naples-new-haven-ike-sewell-pizzeria-uno-lombardi.shtml">American Pie: How a Neapolitan street food became the most successful immigrant of all</a> [American Heritage]</p>



